BMW CarData (HA)
================

This project is a fork and continuation of:

    bmw-cardata-ha (originally published as "BimmerData Streamline")
    Author:  JjyKsi
    Source:  https://github.com/JjyKsi/bmw-cardata-ha

The original author released that work into the public domain, stating in the
project README: "This project is released into the public domain. Do whatever
you want with it ... No attribution required (though appreciated)."

Because the original work carries no licensing restrictions, this fork is
distributed under the MIT License (see the LICENSE file). We nonetheless credit
the original author here, as a matter of courtesy and respect for their work.

Changes in this fork include a rebrand to "BMW CarData (HA)" (domain
`bmw_cardata`), alignment with the published BMW CarData API specification,
additional API endpoints, and a security and code-quality review.

Trademark note: "BMW", "Mini", "Rolls-Royce" and "CarData" are trademarks of
their respective owners. This project is an independent, community-built Home
Assistant integration and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by
BMW Group.
